todo.value: Buy milk from the grocery store.
Call the dentist to schedule a cleaning appointment.
Take out the trash before leaving the house.
Water the plants in the garden.
Send a birthday card to your friend.'
Read 10 pages of a book before going to bed.
Write a gratitude journal entry for the day.
Meditate for 10 minutes in the morning.
Go for a 15-minute walk around the block.
Declutter your desk by organizing papers and supplies.
Make a grocery list for the upcoming week.
Clean out your email inbox and respond to important messages.
Do a load of laundry and fold clothes.
Prepare a healthy lunch for tomorrow.
Write a letter or email to someone you haven't talked to in a while.
